OL,3,CBrides' 'nightmare' after wedding
OL,4,Cdress shop's sudden closure
OL,6,FBrides-to-be say they have been left
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds out of pocket
OL,8,Fafter a West Yorkshire bridal shop
OL,9,Fsuddenly closed down.
OL,11,FAbbey Bridal, in Pontefract, contacted
OL,12,Fcustomers earlier this month to say it
OL,13,Fwas shutting due to "the rapidly
OL,14,Fdeclining economic state of the United
OL,15,FKingdom".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782155909
OL,3,CBrides' 'nightmare' after wedding
OL,4,Cdress shop's sudden closure
OL,6,FCustomer Madeline Roberts said she had
OL,7,Fpaid #2,500 for a wedding dress, but
OL,8,Fhad been warned of a "soft closure"
OL,9,Fwhich would take place over several
OL,10,Fmonths and that refunds could not be
OL,11,Fguaranteed.
OL,13,F"Even though I didn't even get a
OL,14,Freceipt or an invoice, there was no
OL,15,Fpart of me that would ever think that
OL,16,Fyou could walk into a bridal shop and
OL,17,Fsomething like this could happen," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782155909
OL,3,CBrides' 'nightmare' after wedding
OL,4,Cdress shop's sudden closure
OL,6,F"We like to think it's (the dress) the
OL,7,Fbiggest part of the day. Not everybody
OL,8,Fhas got the money to just go and buy
OL,9,Fthemselves another dress."
OL,11,FSince the announcement of the store's
OL,12,Fclosure, she said has received no
OL,13,Frefund and little communication.
OL,15,FAnother bride-to-be, Rhiannon Law,
OL,16,Fsaid she had received a damaged sample
OL,17,Fdress and that she would have to buy a
OL,18,Freplacement.
OL,26,@nD@XpmnD@bpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782155909
OL,3,CBrides' 'nightmare' after wedding
OL,4,Cdress shop's sudden closure
OL,6,F"(Sample dresses) are not worth a lot
OL,7,Fof money because they've been tried on
OL,8,Fby a numerous amount of people," she
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"I don't ever plan on doing this
OL,12,F(getting married) again.
OL,14,F"You want it to be right and you want
OL,15,Fit to be okay. If I wanted a sample
OL,16,Fdress, I would have bought one and
OL,17,Fpaid that price for one."
OL,19,FShe said the whole experience has been
OL,20,F"an absolute nightmare", with her
OL,21,Fwedding three weeks away.
OL,26,@nD@BpmnD@QpntD@ApmtD@Qpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782155909
OL,3,CBrides' 'nightmare' after wedding
OL,4,Cdress shop's sudden closure
OL,6,F"All I've done is cry. All I've done
OL,7,Fis be an emotional wreck."
OL,9,FAbbey Bridal has been approached for a
OL,10,Fcomment.
OL,12,FIn a post on their website its owner,
OL,13,FJessica Sykes said she had recently
OL,14,Fsuffered serious illness but was
OL,15,Fworking to put things right.
OL,17,FThe post said: "Due to the rapidly
OL,18,Fdeclining economic state of the United
OL,19,FKingdom, it is with deepest regret, we
OL,20,Fhave chosen to close the doors for the
OL,21,Flast time at Abbey Bridal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782155909
OL,3,CBrides' 'nightmare' after wedding
OL,4,Cdress shop's sudden closure
OL,6,F"It has become clear to me that the
OL,7,Flonger we wait, the worse the cost of
OL,8,Fliving crisis gets. Your budgets are
OL,9,Flower, and you are having more
OL,10,Fintimate weddings and this has had a
OL,11,Fmajor impact on the bridal industry.
OL,13,F"In the last few months there have
OL,14,Fbeen a number of bridal businesses in
OL,15,FYorkshire alone that have closed their
OL,16,Fdoors and it has become clear that I
OL,17,Fam just putting off the inevitable.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782155909
OL,3,CBrides' 'nightmare' after wedding
OL,4,Cdress shop's sudden closure
OL,6,F"For my mental health, for my
OL,7,Fchildren's, it is time. I didn't
OL,8,Fsurvive cancer, just to survive and be
OL,9,Fin constant worry."
OL,11,FShe said she was working through
OL,12,Frefund requests.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/7
